Title: Les Misérables
Writer: Ladj Ly (screenplay), Giordano Gederlini (screenplay), Alexis Manenti (screenplay)
Actors: Damien Bonnard, Alexis Manenti, Djebril Zonga, Issa Perica
Plot: A cop from the provinces moves to Paris to join the Anti-Crime Brigade of Montfermeil, discovering an underworld where the tensions between the different groups mark the rhythm.
Awards: Nominated for 1 Oscar. Another 14 wins & 46 nominations.
